      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0024",
      "text": ": Logical N_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        146.46,
        190.97,
        227.87,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0025",
      "text": " In this state the N_Port operates as VFT tagging N_Port. FC frames",
      "bbox": [
        228.0,
        190.97,
        539.96,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 4
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0026",
      "text": "transmitted by the N_Port are tagged with the VFT_Header carrying VF_ID K. The Logical N_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.97,
        539.82,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0027",
      "text": "continues its operations. The Logical N_Port may acquire additional N_Port_IDs in Virtual Fabric K",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.97,
        539.98,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0028",
      "text": "by following the N_Port_ID virtualization procedure.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.97,
        323.18,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0029",
      "text": "Transition P4:P1.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.97,
        177.68,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0030",
      "text": " Occurs when the EVFP processing determined that VFT tagging is not performed",
      "bbox": [
        177.66,
        250.97,
        540.13,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0031",
      "text": "and the N_Port and F_Port have the same Port VF_ID. In state P1 the N_Port shall repeat the FLOGI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.97,
        540.1,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0032",
      "text": "process with the Virtual Fabrics bit set to zero in the FLOGI request, in order to acquire an N_Port_ID",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        540.02,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0033",
      "text": "in the Virtual Fabric identified by the Port VF_ID.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        309.81,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0034",
      "text": "Transition P4:P8.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        177.68,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0035",
      "text": " Occurs when the EVFP processing determined that VFT tagging is not performed",
      "bbox": [
        177.66,
        310.96,
        540.13,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0036",
      "text": "and the N_Port and F_Port do not have the same Port VF_ID.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        369.26,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0037",
      "text": "State P8: Isolated.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        182.09,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0038",
      "text": " In this state the N_Port is offline.",
      "bbox": [
        182.1,
        346.96,
        328.71,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0039",
      "text": "When VFT tagging is enabled on a link, a Link Reset (see FC-FS-2) shall not change the tagging pro-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        540.04,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0040",
      "text": "cess, while a Link Initialization (see FC-FS-2) shall stop the tagging process and reinitialize the link.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        534.73,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p206_s0041",
      "text": "8.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        109.88,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
